<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="vi">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>SmartSpend AI - Quản lý chi tiêu thông minh</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.11.0/font/bootstrap-icons.css">
    <style>
        body {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8f9fa 0%, #e0e7ff 100%);
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
        }
        .hero-section {
            flex: 1;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-light bg-white shadow-sm py-3">
        <div class="container">
            <a class="navbar-brand fw-bold text-primary fs-4" href="/">
                <i class="bi bi-wallet2 me-2"></i>SmartSpend AI
            </a>
            <div>
                <a href="/auth/login" class="btn btn-outline-primary me-2 fw-bold px-4 rounded-pill">Đăng nhập</a>
                <a href="/auth/register" class="btn btn-primary fw-bold px-4 rounded-pill shadow-sm">Đăng ký</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <div class="hero-section text-center py-5">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row justify-content-center">
                <div class="col-lg-8">
                    <div class="mb-4 d-inline-block p-3 rounded-circle bg-white shadow-sm">
                        <i class="bi bi-robot text-primary" style="font-size: 4rem;"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h1 class="display-4 fw-bold text-dark mb-4">Quản lý chi tiêu thông minh với <span class="text-primary">Trợ lý AI</span></h1>
                    <p class="lead text-muted mb-5 px-md-5">Ghi chép giao dịch bằng giọng nói, phân tích chi tiêu tự động và cảnh báo vượt hạn mức. Giúp bạn làm chủ tài chính dễ dàng hơn bao giờ hết.</p>
                    
                    <div class="d-flex justify-content-center gap-3 flex-wrap">
                        <a href="/auth/register" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg rounded-pill px-5 shadow fw-bold">
                            Bắt đầu ngay <i class="bi bi-arrow-right ms-2"></i>
                        </a>
                        <a href="/dashboard" class="btn btn-light border btn-lg rounded-pill px-5 fw-bold text-secondary shadow-sm hover-primary">
                            Vào Dashboard
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <footer class="bg-white text-center py-4 mt-auto border-top">
        <p class="text-muted small mb-0 fw-semibold">&copy; 2026 SmartSpend AI Project - Powered by FPT AI & MongoDB Atlas</p>
    </footer>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>